          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Our next adventure in Peru was a ten hour train ride north from Puno to Cusco. We had really been looking forward to this day because we had heard so many great things about this train ride from our friends. I'm so happy we chose to travel from Puno to Cusco by rail because we were able to look out the window at various parts of the Peruvian countryside that we wouldn't have seen otherwise and chat with some fellow travelers."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Since we had purchased our Peru Rail tickets for the "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://www.perurail.com/andean-explorer",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "Andean Explorer"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " in advance, the check-in process was a breeze. Once we arrived at the station, we just had to wait in a short line to get our tickets and passports verified, and then we had a short 15 minute wait before boarding."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
