          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " Quite the range of entertainment was offered throughout the day. There was both a morning and afternoon concert by two different bands - one from Puno and one from Cusco. A woman in traditional dress accompanied both of the bands and danced. Additionally, there was as also a short fashion show and a demonstration on how to make Pisco Sours."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
