                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " The train stopped one time during our journey at La Raya, the highest point of the trip. We were able to get out and shop around at a little market and peek into an old church. I was so excited to get a picture with this cute little girl and baby lamb!"
          }
