      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "If you are planning a trip to Peru and you have the time, I highly recommend you book your journey between Puno and Cusco on the Andean Explorer! It was such a neat experience and the perfect way to see parts of the country you might not otherwise see. It was one of the big highlights of our trip!"
          }
